### Nutrition Profile MVP smoke tests
### Base URL (zmień jeśli backend działa na innym porcie/hoście)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@authPrefix = /api/v1/auth
@profilePrefix = /api/v1/profile
@conversationsPrefix = /api/v1/conversations

### Dane testowego użytkownika
@email = nutrition.demo@example.com
@password = StrongPass123

### =========================
### 1) Register
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}{{authPrefix}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### =========================
### 2) Login (zapis tokena do zmiennej)
### =========================
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}{{authPrefix}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("access_token", response.body.access_token);
%}

### =========================
### 3) Get profile przed utworzeniem
### Oczekiwane: 404 + code NOT_FOUND
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}{{profilePrefix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### =========================
### 4) Create profile (z harmonogramem tygodniowym — Faza 9)
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}{{profilePrefix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 29,
  "height_cm": 187,
  "weight_kg": 80,
  "activity_level": "HIGH",
  "goal": "MUSCLE_GAIN",
  "diet_type": "VEGETARIAN",
  "weekly_obligations": [
    {
      "day_of_week": "MON",
      "start_time": "09:00:00",
      "end_time": "17:00:00",
      "label": "Work"
    },
    {
      "day_of_week": "WED",
      "start_time": "18:00:00",
      "end_time": "19:00:00",
      "label": "Training"
    }
  ]
}

### =========================
### 5) Get profile po utworzeniu — powinien zawierać weekly_obligations
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}{{profilePrefix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### =========================
### 6) Negatywny test: utworzenie drugiego profilu
### Oczekiwane: 409 + code CONFLICT
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}{{profilePrefix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 29,
  "height_cm": 187,
  "weight_kg": 80,
  "activity_level": "HIGH",
  "goal": "MUSCLE_GAIN",
  "diet_type": "VEGETARIAN"
}

### =========================
### 7) Update profile (częściowy — tylko wskazane pola się zmieniają)
### =========================
PUT {{baseUrl}}{{profilePrefix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weight_kg": 82,
  "activity_level": "VERY_HIGH"
}

### =========================
### 8) Update: wyczyść harmonogram tygodniowy (pusta lista = brak, nie "bez zmian")
### =========================
PUT {{baseUrl}}{{profilePrefix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weekly_obligations": []
}

### =========================
### 9) Negatywny test: end_time <= start_time w weekly_obligations
### Oczekiwane: 400 + code BAD_REQUEST (walidacja domenowa, nie schema — patrz architecture.md)
### =========================
PUT {{baseUrl}}{{profilePrefix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weekly_obligations": [
    {
      "day_of_week": "MON",
      "start_time": "17:00:00",
      "end_time": "09:00:00",
      "label": "Bad range"
    }
  ]
}

### =========================
### 10) Negatywny test: nieprawidłowy wiek
### Oczekiwane: 422 + code VALIDATION_ERROR
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}{{profilePrefix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 200,
  "height_cm": 187,
  "weight_kg": 80,
  "activity_level": "HIGH",
  "goal": "MUSCLE_GAIN",
  "diet_type": "VEGETARIAN"
}

### =========================
### 11) Negatywny test: brak tokena
### Oczekiwane: 401 + code INVALID_ACCESS_TOKEN
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}{{profilePrefix}}

### =========================
### 12) Drugi użytkownik — bez profilu (izolacja danych)
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}{{authPrefix}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nutrition.other@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123"
}

###
# @name loginOther
POST {{baseUrl}}{{authPrefix}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nutrition.other@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("other_access_token", response.body.access_token);
%}

### =========================
### 13) Drugi user nie widzi cudzego profilu
### Oczekiwane: 404 + code NOT_FOUND (własny profil nie istnieje)
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}{{profilePrefix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{other_access_token}}

### =========================
### 14) Weryfikacja: profil wpływa na odpowiedź AI
### Utwórz konwersację i wyślij wiadomość — odpowiedź powinna
### uwzględniać ustawiony profil (np. VEGETARIAN z kroku 4/7).
### =========================
# @name createConversation
POST {{baseUrl}}{{conversationsPrefix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dinner ideas",
  "category": "DIET"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("conversation_id", response.body.conversation_id);
%}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}{{conversationsPrefix}}/{{conversation_id}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "What should I eat for dinner tonight?"
}
